OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776265866
OL,3,CLocal election postponed following
OL,4,Cdeath of Reform candidate
OL,6,FOne of the planned local elections has
OL,7,Fbeen delayed following the death of a
OL,8,Fcandidate.
OL,10,FAndrew John Feeney was standing as the
OL,11,FReform Candidate in the St Helens Town
OL,12,FCentre ward, which has now been
OL,13,Fpostponed due to his death.
OL,15,FAll other St Helens borough ward
OL,16,Felections will continue as planned on
OL,17,FThursday 7 May 2026 along with a
OL,18,Fnumber of other local elections across
OL,19,Fthe country.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
