OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776265866
OL,3,CLocal election postponed following
OL,4,Cdeath of Reform candidate
OL,6,FOnly the ballot for Town Centre ward
OL,7,Fhas been postponed and voters in that
OL,8,Farea will get a letter explaining when
OL,9,Fthey'll get their chance to elect
OL,10,Ftheir councillor.
OL,12,FA new date for the election is being
OL,13,Farranged, which will be no more than
OL,14,F35 working days after the original
OL,15,Fpolling day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
