PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776265866
OL,3,CLocal election postponed following
OL,4,Cdeath of Reform candidate
OL,6,FMark Palethorpe, Returning Officer for
OL,7,FSt Helens Borough Council said: "We
OL,8,Fsend our condolences to Andrew's
OL,9,Ffamily at this sad time. Legally, we
OL,10,Fmust now postpone the election in St
OL,11,FHelens Town Centre Ward.
OL,13,F"I have already contacted the other
OL,14,Fcandidates and will be writing to all
OL,15,Faffected electors in the ward."
OL,26,@oD@aOUwD@_O]
