OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776265866
OL,3,CLocal election postponed following
OL,4,Cdeath of Reform candidate
OL,6,FNew poll cards will be sent to all
OL,7,Faffected voters once the date is set.
OL,8,FThey will tell voters how to arrange a
OL,9,Fpostal or proxy vote if they cannot
OL,10,Fmake it to the polling station on the
OL,11,Fnew date.
OL,13,FCandidate nominations will reopen for
OL,14,Fa set period once the new date is
OL,15,Fannounced. All other previous
OL,16,Fcandidates remain validly nominated
OL,17,Fand will be included on the ballot
OL,18,Fpaper.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
